                    div.article_description
                        div.article_description_title
                            h4 EPA Plans to Clean Up Troubled Chemical and Pesticide Programs 
                            div.byline1
                                span.author
                                    span(style="box-sizing: border-box;") Matthew Teelucksingh - 
                                span(title="October 13 2021", style="box-sizing: border-box;") Oct 13 2021
                            div.byline2
                                span.categories
                                    span(style="box-sizing: border-box;") Cold War History
                                    span(style="box-sizing: border-box;") Strategy  
                                    span(style="box-sizing: border-box;") Political Science
                        div.article_summary
                            p.summary_paragraph Community advocates and environmental groups pointed out that the EPA has promised action on toxic PFAS pollution for many years.
